google.subtitle: Ruling Passion
google.description: Passions - Ruling Passion By Katherine Kingston During a daring raid to rescue prisoners he was hired to free, Lord Jeoffrey Blaisdell discovers Lady Rosalind Hamilton. To secure her own release as well, she agrees to his price, though she knows she cannot pay it. When he learns of her deception, Jeoffrey offers her an alternate price for rescue... The payment is to be reaped by Lord Jeoffrey in his bedchambers-swiftly, immediately, and all night long.
